<component type="desktop-application">
  <id>org.mechanicalflower.Marble</id>

  <name>Marble</name>
  <summary>A marble race minigame, made with Godot Engine.</summary>

  <metadata_license>CC-BY-SA-4.0</metadata_license>
  <project_license>MIT</project_license>

  <description>
    <p>Marble is an  open source mini-game about marble racing.</p>
    <h2>Controls</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>WASD - Move</li>
      <li>Tab - Follow a marble</li>
      <li>ESC - Return to Menu</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Features</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Name your marbles</li>
      <li>Start procedural races</li>
      <li>Watch the real-time ranking</li>
    </ul>
    <p>The game is made with the open source Godot Engine. The source code and assets are MIT licensed.</p>
  </description>

